settings.privacy:
The products sold on www.amouage.com are picked and carefully packed by our colleagues in our Omani Manufacture and shipped to 63 countries worldwide. We are always looking at ways to improve our service, including extending our geographical coverage. If your country is not yet part of our list, please sign-up to our newsletter receive future updates.

Once you place an order, you will automatically receive a confirmation email with your order confirmation number, the details of your purchase and additional key information.

Our staff will pick and pack the items you ordered and hand the parcel to our partner, DHL, which will ship it to your chosen address. At this point, you will automatically receive an email with a tracking number.

You may check the status of your order at any time by visiting the DHL website and using your tracking number.

Please, note that your order status may take up to 48 hours to update after your order has been placed and up to 72 during the weekend. During national and religious holidays, please allow for an additional delay.

Shipments to the United States are handled by either DHL or FedEx. If your shipping confirmation email mentioned FedEx, you can track your order on the FedEx website by clicking on "Tracking" in the menu and inserting the tracking number received via email.

We do offer Standard International Delivery on all orders shipped from Oman and Standard Ground Delivery on orders shipped from the United States.Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
